        <body><div type="bibliography">
                
                <p>Fragment a: <bibl><ptr target="#gpc1961"/>, p. 30, n. <citedRange>10</citedRange> (from †Oliverio's papers), fig. 19</bibl>, whence 
                    <bibl><ptr target="#SEG"/>, <citedRange>20.721, a</citedRange></bibl>;
                    fragment b: not published before <bibl><ptr target="#IGCyr"/> <citedRange>064500</citedRange></bibl>.</p>
            <p>Cf. <bibl><ptr target="#rosamilia2023"/>, pp. <citedRange>129-130</citedRange>.</bibl></p>
            </div><div type="edition" xml:lang="grc" xml:space="preserve">
                
              
